beer.beer_description: Nomad and beer cartel have come togetjer to brew up some christmas cheer with this delicious Red IPA. With the use of specialty malts to give a deep red colour and pine-y hops such as Simcoe,Chinook and dr Rudi to make you feel like you’re walking into a pine forest laden with christmas lanterns.

items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 15 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 4!

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 30 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 7!
